sentence: salesforce.com, inc. ( CRM ) has moved higher as of late, but there could definitely be trouble on the horizon for this company.
That is because CRM is now in overbought territory with an RSI value of 72.02.
Furthermore, estimates for the salesforce.com, inc have been coming down, pushing it to a Zacks Rank #5 (Strong Sell).
This suggests that investors may better off exiting this stock before it falls back to Earth.
